snippet.title: Sega Smash Pack PC - 64 Bit Windows (Part 1)
snippet.description: A quick look at getting the fairly rare Sega Smash Pack PC to run on 64 bit Windows. I'll be modernizing and patching it a bit in my free time whenever I get the chance. This just took me a couple of minutes of work, so nothing too serious yet.
